  "texts": [
    "The purpose of the task is to process the input data entirely.",
    "Generally, the input and output data are collections of files, but there are also other formats, such as a group of sequence numbers, metadata, a collection of sub-file data, or notifications.",
    "Job and WorkerA job is a PanDA object with distinct states that corresponds a sub-unit of a workload partitioned from a task.",
    "A single task consists of multiple jobs, and each job is executed by a worker, which is an abstraction of the execution point, such as a worker node and CPU cluster.",
    "A worker refers to a software program or a collection of software programs that assumes the responsibility of executing one or more jobs on computing resources."
